Senate Resolution 267
By: Senator James of the 28th
A RESOLUTION
1 Honoring the life of Ms. Aj'anaye Hill and dedicating an intersection in her memory; and for
2 other purposes.
3 WHEREAS, Ms. Aj'anaye Hill was born in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania, on April 1, 2008, the
4 beloved daughter of Chanell White and Louis Hill; and
5 WHEREAS, Ms. Hill was a loved and talented student at Lithia Springs High School, with
6 an expected graduation date of 2026; and
7 WHEREAS, she had a passion for music and dancing and enjoyed making TikTok videos
8 with her family and friends; and
9 WHEREAS, Ms. Hill's life was tragically cut short on March 4, 2023, when she was one of
10 ten children shot at a sweet 16 birthday party in Douglas County; and
11 WHEREAS, known for her outspoken and fearless nature, Ms. Hill will long be remembered
12 for her love of family and friendship, and this loyal daughter and friend will be missed by all
13 who had the great fortune of knowing her; and
