14 WHEREAS, it is abundantly fitting and proper that this remarkable and distinguished
15 Georgian be recognized appropriately by dedicating an intersection in her memory.
16 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED AND ENACTED BY THE GENERAL
17 ASSEMBLY OF GEORGIA that the intersection of U.S. 78 and Campbellton Street in
18 Douglas County is dedicated as the Aj'anaye Hill Memorial Intersection.
19 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Department of Transportation is authorized and
20 directed to erect and maintain appropriate signs dedicating the Aj'anaye Hill Memorial
21 Intersection.
22 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Secretary of the Senate is authorized and directed
23 to make appropriate copies of this resolution available for distribution to the family of Ms.
24 Aj'anaye Hill and to the Department of Transportation.
